title: Mortal Kombat 1 Quan Chi Official Gameplay Trailer
description:
The power of the NetherRealm is at his fingertips. Beware his sorcery. Quan Chi arrives in Mortal Kombat for Early Access on December 14, Full Release December 21. Khameleon joins the kameo roster in January 2024.

title: Fortnite - Peter Griffin Seeks Fitness Advice from Meowscles Hybrid Short
description:
Peter Griffin seeks fitness advice and finds himself in Fortnite: 

What happens when family guy Peter Griffin seeks out fitness advice from a cartoon cat? Check out how Peter finds his way into Fortnite with a sneak peek of gameplay action in Fortnite Battle Royale.
